1#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">Spring Boot 集成 WebSocket 并实现简易聊天室</a></p><p><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247484059&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=65ad032dcc76206fe582d1712753509d&amp;chksm=ea770104dd008812cbd19f584460f4a0488b96eb5b3b80514ba5a85cd023c6b3495f1cd58ad6&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">浅谈布式锁及其实现的几种方式</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><a href=\"http://www.imcoder.fun//archives/%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5java%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%A3annotation%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%A3\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">深入JAVA注解(Annotation)以及自定义注解</a></p><p><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247484007&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=01306ebefa610ef2fe1cfc2359243c83&amp;chksm=ea7701f8dd0088ee538aacdddd44fa4ad032dd38d7356e9c586f4f5866a3df825f3218de7d5e&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">面试中经常被JAVA多线程虐的看过来！</a></p><p><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247484007&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=25853598e1407a8bbab742bf9966f9d8&amp;chksm=ea7701f8dd0088ee7dca556d99989bde864bc4095abee64b66be6dfe2153b4c26f1c94a2e188&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">vue 常用插件集合</a></p><p><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247483982&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=acec6698b45f268a71e0e06349bb1639&amp;chksm=ea7701d1dd0088c7bc24b2de2f113d23ef59113c58a45c96730e9c701d2d86dc42b84c940d3f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">Spring Cloud 微服务实战 -- 注册中心 Eureka</a></p><p><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247483883&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=cb11a1cbddbcdace7a307ca00f41a023&amp;chksm=ea770274dd008b6201b64eaa4231e5689b3b8215612814a5e40d9e313efbe060feb06b096602&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">Spring Cloud 微服务实战 -- 微服务构建 SpringBoot</a></p><p><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247483897&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7fc9eb43cc93f605d069030c90228af1&amp;chksm=ea770266dd008b70df29b0e6d3f6f1fcbc06df019af13b82f64c56fc617ac557a29d07b43798&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">Java多线程：彻底搞懂线程池</a></p><p><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247483781&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c0989a4d9804ffe02c380279c0277b7a&amp;chksm=ea77021add008b0c52622b742399e3d88baf711e9f2d464a0e699695f07abbee8bae7094df37&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">你还在用 Java6 的写法来使用 Java8 么？</a></p><p><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247483761&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=85190bc39beb3796e7c6b49b938f8946&amp;chksm=ea7702eedd008bf83eaf79a8469789dc713522c474c676b2b3ceea84397d6e1ef47b11f709c2&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">用Gradle从零开始搭建Springboot+Mybatis工程</a></p>', '<h2><strong>装饰者模式介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">装饰者模式是指动态的给对象添加一些职责，其重点是动态扩展对象的功能；就增加功能来说，装饰者模式比生成子类更为灵活。</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><h2><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">使用场景</strong></h2><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">在不影响其他对象的情况下，以动态、透明的方式给单个对象添加职责。</span></li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">需要动态地给一个对象增加功能，这些功能也可以动态地被撤销。</span></li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">当不能采用继承的方式对系统进行扩充或者采用继承不利于系统扩展和维护时。不能采用继承的情况主要有两类：第一类是系统中存在大量独立的扩展，为支持每一种组合将产生大量的子类，使得子类数目呈爆炸性增长；第二类是因为类定义不能继承（如final类）。</span></li></ul><p><br></p><h2 class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">装饰器结构</strong></h2><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">抽象构件（Component）：定义一个对象接口或抽象类，可以给这些对象动态地添加职责。</span></li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">具体构件（ConcreteComponent）：实际被动态地添加职责的对象。</span></li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">抽象装饰者（Decorator）：实现了Component接口，用来扩展Component类的功能，但对于Component来说，是无需知道Decorator的存在的。</span></li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">具体装饰者（ConcreteDecorator）：动态地添加职责的对象。</span></li></ul><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p>​<img src=\"https://imgconvert.csdnimg.cn/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xcGljLmNuL3N6X21tYml6X3BuZy9Wb3pZd0FpYWdhU0toaFRNNWljY3ViN2p1RlZOdTNVNkJaeGhDSkdicEdNUlNKajhPWkxvUzhMeFNrd2lhQ3dYVXZUa3NsaWF3R2NwdXhTQW9yckNDVEVzNWcvNjQw?x-oss-process=image/format,png\"></p><p><br></p><h2 class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">代码示例</strong></h2><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">人类组件接口（Person）定义了打扮（装饰）的功能，装饰类（Decorator）继承人类的功能，具体的装饰者实现者类（ClothesDecorator，ShoeDecorator，HatDecorator等）继承装饰类，并对其功能进行添加扩展；具体的组件类(Coder)和装饰类一样继承组件接口（Person）；我们可以用具体的装饰类（ClothesDecorator，ShoeDecorator，HatDecorator）将具体的组件类(Coder)进行装饰(添加职责)；</span></p><p>​<img src=\"https://imgconvert.csdnimg.cn/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xcGljLmNuL3N6X21tYml6X3BuZy9Wb3pZd0FpYWdhU0toaFRNNWljY3ViN2p1RlZOdTNVNkJaUENpY0lOYmtJSHVKU3FXaWFiWFY1bGZrdGtBakNERGlib05sdFlHYndkbkR2WTZWZFE0a2NlZWRBLzY0MA?x-oss-process=image/format,png\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">​​</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">人类组件接口（Person）</strong></h3><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">在人类组件接口中定义了一个人类的公共方法-------装饰打扮；</span></p><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">package</span> fun.imcoder.cloud.test;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Author</span> imcoder\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Description</span> 装饰 Person接口\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Date</span> 2020/01/06\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Person</span> </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">decoratePerson</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span></span>;\n}\n\n</pre><p><br></p><h3><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">装饰者（Decorator）</strong></h3><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">装饰者其实就像给父类进行一层包装；将父类装进了自己的构造器，并且实现了父类的装饰方法，在方法内部调用的是父类的同名方法；</span></p><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">package</span> fun.imcoder.cloud.test;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> lombok.Data;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Author</span> imcoder\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Description</span> 装饰者父类\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Date</span> 2020/01/06\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Data</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Decorator</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Person</span> </span>{\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> Person person;\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">decoratePerson</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> </span>{\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (person != <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">null</span>) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 调用父类装饰方法</span>\n            person.decoratePerson();\n        }\n    }\n\n}\n\n</pre><p><br></p><h3><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">具体的装饰者</strong></h3><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">具体的装饰者继承装饰者，理论上是可以无限多个具体的装饰者，取决于你对具体组件类的扩展；具体的装饰者实现父类的方法，并且在内部调用父类的同名方法，还可以在实现方法中添加特有的职责；</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">衣服装饰者</span></p><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">package</span> fun.imcoder.cloud.test;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Author</span> imcoder\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Description</span> 衣服装饰者\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Date</span> 2020/01/06\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">ClothesDecorator</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Decorator</span> </span>{\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">decoratePerson</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> </span>{\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 继承父类装饰</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">super</span>.decoratePerson();\n        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ClothesDecorator给coder穿上衣服！\"</span>);\n    }\n\n}\n</pre><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">鞋子装饰者</span></p><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">package</span> fun.imcoder.cloud.test;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Author</span> imcoder\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Description</span> 鞋子装饰者\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Date</span> 2020/01/06\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">ShoeDecorator</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Decorator</span> </span>{\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">decoratePerson</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> </span>{\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 继承父类装饰</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">super</span>.decoratePerson();\n        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ShoeDecorator给coder穿上鞋子！\"</span>);\n    }\n\n}\n</pre><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">帽子装饰者</span></p><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">package</span> fun.imcoder.cloud.test;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Author</span> imcoder\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Description</span> 帽子装饰者\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Date</span> 2020/01/06\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">HatDecorator</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Decorator</span> </span>{\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">decoratePerson</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> </span>{\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 继承父类装饰</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">super</span>.decoratePerson();\n        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"HatDecorator给coder带上帽子！\"</span>);\n    }\n\n}\n</pre><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">具体的组件类</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">具体的组件类实现组件接口；</span></p><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">package</span> fun.imcoder.cloud.test;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Author</span> imcoder\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Description</span> 程序员类，实现要装饰的人\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@Date</span> 2020/01/06\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Coder</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Person</span> </span>{\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Override</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">decoratePerson</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> </span>{\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 装饰开始</span>\n        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"hello coder的自我修养，现在装饰开始啦！\"</span>);\n    }\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">main</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(String[] args)</span> </span>{\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 创建一个程序员 coder</span>\n        Coder coder = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> Coder();\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 创建衣服装饰器</span>\n        ClothesDecorator clothesDecorator = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ClothesDecorator();\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 创建鞋子装饰器</span>\n        ShoeDecorator shoeDecorator = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ShoeDecorator();\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 创建帽子装饰器</span>\n        HatDecorator hatDecorator = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> HatDecorator();\n\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 给coder穿上衣服</span>\n        clothesDecorator.setPerson(coder);\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 给coder穿上鞋子</span>\n        shoeDecorator.setPerson(clothesDecorator);\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 给coder戴上帽子</span>\n        hatDecorator.setPerson(shoeDecorator);\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 执行装饰</span>\n        hatDecorator.decoratePerson();\n        System.out.println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"装饰结束！\"</span>);\n    }\n}\n</pre><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">执行结果</span></p><p>​<img src=\"https://imgconvert.csdnimg.cn/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xcGljLmNuL3N6X21tYml6X3BuZy9Wb3pZd0FpYWdhU0toaFRNNWljY3ViN2p1RlZOdTNVNkJaYjd6V2V6ZUlYOEduaWJOTk5TM0xNcE5kOTBMNFNXaHJna1RWZEpZWk9DQWliWDNHUXR2aWFCcGlhdy82NDA?x-oss-process=image/format,png\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">在进行装饰的时候可以看见是将具体的装饰套在了具体组件类身上；有多少个具体装饰类就可以自由组合多少次套装具体装饰类身上，就等于添加了多少个职责；</span></p><p><br></p><h2 class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">优点</strong></h2><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">装饰者模式和继承关系的目的都是要扩展对象的功能，但是装饰模式可以提供比继承更多的灵活性。</span></li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">通过使用不同的具体装饰者类及它们不同的组合顺序，可以得到不同装饰后具有不同行为或者状态的对象。</span></li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">符合开闭原则。</span></li></ul><p><br></p><h2><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">缺点</strong></h2><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">增加了抽象装饰者类和具体装饰者类，一定程度增加了系统的复杂度，加大了系统的学习和理解成本。</span></li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-size: 15px;\">灵活性也意味着更容易出错，对于多次被多次修饰的对象，调试时寻找错误可能需要找到多个地方。</span></li></ul><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://imgconvert.csdnimg.cn/aHR0cHM6Ly91cGxvYWQtaW1hZ2VzLmppYW5zaHUuaW8vdXBsb2FkX2ltYWdlcy8yMDI2MzQzNS04NWVkODFjNzdjNTY3YTJj?x-oss-process=image/format,png\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 0);\">往期文章</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247484139&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=deb1677796ece74fe83aafe4ddefd4f2&amp;chksm=ea770174dd008862bc6eca56af468ee1cff5dda3fd75bad395cb859d744b6c5457cf8ac4cd0b&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">记一次Linux挖矿病毒的清除与原因分析</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247484130&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=aa747be82a087c387c8fe9f131bf2fe6&amp;chksm=ea77017ddd00886b0e128138cca12847ec5d32ac15b9a330ab2221194e22cd384f465e1f0a07&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">Redis实现高并发分布式锁</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247484145&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c76c10934f119a4ddfc4983e83fc5190&amp;chksm=ea77016edd008878571bb8f9c60a1881ef48ce3d5ea12c957f844f0c590c856970888ca35900&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">Java设计模式 -- 单例模式</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=2247484146&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=eef52ffb1a7cc3c42ed4d032353051f1&amp;chksm=ea77016ddd00887b666ada79ebae770846eb366a41a3dbea7799f3d1e4849afe5364eed4236b&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(87, 107, 149);\">Java设计模式 -- 代理模式</a></p><p><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1OTYxMDM1Mg==&amp;mid=22