INSERT INTO `content` VALUES (29, '发布自己的项目到Maven中央仓库详细图文教程', '最近自己写了个小工具，由于项目中多次用到，并且式自己业余作品，所以不能发布到公司私有maven仓库，于是想到发布到maven中央仓库。&nbsp;https://issues.sonatype.org/secure/Dashboard.js', '<p><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">最近自己写了个小工具，由于项目中多次用到，本着开源的精神，于是想到发布到maven中央仓库。发现虽然网上的教程不少，大多都千篇一律，遇到问题不知道该如何处理。</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">下面我介绍一下自己的</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(240, 102, 102);\" class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">亲身发布</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">过程。</span></p><p><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">发布过程大概有以下步骤：</span></p><ol><li><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">注册sonatype账号</span></li><li><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">在</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\" class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">sonatype中</span><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">新建issue</span></li><li><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">等待审核回复并验证groupId</span></li><li><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">创建gpg密钥并且发送密钥</span></li><li><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">配置maven POM并deploy和release</span></li></ol><p><br></p><h2><strong class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">注册sonatype账号</strong></h2><blockquote><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">Sonatype是一个通过Nexus对开源项目提供托管服务的网站。你可以通过它发布项目的快照（snapshot）或者稳定版本（release）到Maven中央仓库。我们只需要注册一个Sonatype的账号，新建一个issue，然后在项目的pom文件中进行配置即可。</span></blockquote><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">注册地址：</span><a href=\"https://issues.sonatype.org/secure/Dashboard.jspa\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">https://issues.sonatype.org/secure/Dashboard.jspa</a></p><p><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200305191547133.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2NoZW5kb25nZG9uZzE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" height=\"428\" width=\"1289\"></span></p><p>如果有账号的话可以直接登录，没有账号的话点击Sign up注册，我这里已经注册过了，直接登录就好。</p><p><br></p><h2><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">新建issue</strong></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">登录进去之后我们点击新建</span></p><p>​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200305191807863.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2NoZW5kb25nZG9uZzE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" height=\"531\" width=\"1298\"></p><p>接下来会弹出一个框，我们依次填入信息就好</p><p>在此之前你需要有一个github仓库来存放你的代码，下图是我的代码仓库，也欢迎大家前去访问</p><p>https://github.com/imcoder-cloud/imcoder-base</p><p>​​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/202003051922145.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2NoZW5kb25nZG9uZzE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" height=\"893\" width=\"726\"></p><p>​​问题类型选 New Project，填入你的概要、描述、等信息，注意：Group Id尤为重要，填写完毕并提交后，会给你发送一封邮件让你验证你是否拥有此域，例如我填的是fun.imcoder.cloud，他会问我是否拥有imcoder.fun的所有权。</p><p>​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200305193039259.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2NoZW5kb25nZG9uZzE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" height=\"713\" width=\"1071\"></p><p>由于imcoder.fun是我自己的域名，所以进行了域名验证。</p><p><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">这里一定要注意如果你有自己的域名的话，你的Group Id一定要反过来写，即fun.imcoder.cloud，后面的cloud是可以加的。</span></p><p><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">这里有两条验证方法</span></p><ol><li><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">给自己的域名添加一条TXT类型的记录</span></li><li><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">重定向到你的GitHub页面</span></li></ol><p><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">我选择是第一种方法，强烈建议你拥有一个自己的域名</span></p><p><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">解析如下</span></p><p>​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200305193811821.png\" height=\"90\" width=\"813\"></p><p><br></p><p>配置完成后回复他们已经配置完成，请他们验证。</p><p>​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200305195827960.png\" height=\"163\" width=\"863\"></p><p><br></p><p>接下来他们验证通过后会给你回复，并且问题的状态会变为已解决。</p><p>​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200305195930616.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2NoZW5kb25nZG9uZzE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" height=\"216\" width=\"727\"></p><p>​​​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200305195954236.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2NoZW5kb25nZG9uZzE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" height=\"342\" width=\"847\"></p><p><br></p><p>然后记得回复并把问题关闭，接着会给你再发次邮件，告诉你发布<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">成功</span>后，你的项目通常会在10分钟之内同步到maven中央仓库。</p><p>​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200306101658901.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2NoZW5kb25nZG9uZzE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" height=\"519\" width=\"1549\"></p><p>详细issue链接：<a href=\"https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/OSSRH-55586\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/OSSRH-55586</a></p><p><br></p><h2><strong class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">创建gpg密钥并且发送密钥</strong></h2><h3><strong>安装</strong></h3><p>​​<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">gpg（GunPG）是一款用于生成秘钥的加密软件。Windows下载地址：</span><a href=\"https://www.gpg4win.org/download.html \" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(6, 129, 208);\">https://www.gpg4win.org/download.html</a><a href=\"https://www.gpg4win.org/download.html \" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">&nbsp;</a></p><p>windows的安装很简单下载完成后一路下一步就好。</p><p>安装完成后验证以下，输入如下命令</p><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-attribute\">gpg</span> --version\n</pre><p><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">​​</span>​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200305200441800.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2NoZW5kb25nZG9uZzE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" height=\"510\" width=\"976\"></p><p>​​</p><h3><strong class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">​​生成密钥</strong></h3><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-attribute\">gpg</span> --gen-key\n</pre><p><br></p><p>接下来会让你输入真实名称、邮箱</p><p>​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200305200902351.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2NoZW5kb25nZG9uZzE=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" height=\"508\" width=\"959\"></p><p><br></p><p>21A78F78088627FBFDF44B0AF454587F5B01700C就是生成的密钥</p><p>​​然后设置PassPhrase密码，如下图。一定要牢记你设置的密码，下面会用到</p><p>​<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200305200821325.png\" height=\"212\" width=\"281\"></p><p><br></p><h3><strong>上传密钥</strong></h3><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-attribute\">gpg</span> --keyserver hkp://keyserver.ubuntu.com:11371 --send-keys 21A78F78088627FBFDF44B0AF454587F5B01700C\n</pre><p><br></p><p>上传后可以通过如下命令查询</p><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">gpg</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">--list-keys</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\">gpg:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">checking</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">the</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">trustdb</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\">gpg: marginals needed:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\">completes needed:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\">trust model:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">pgp</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\">gpg: depth:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-string\">valid:</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-string\">signed:</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\">trust:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">-,</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">0q,</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">0n,</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">0m,</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">0f,</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">2u</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\">gpg:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">next</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">trustdb</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">check</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">due</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">at</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2022-03-05</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-string\">C:/Users/11879/AppData/Roaming/gnupg/pubring.kbx</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-string\">------------------------------------------------</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-string\">pub</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-string\">rsa2048</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2020-03-05</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">[SC]</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">[expires:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2022-03-05</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">]</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-string\">78C42AF52F1A261BC7116AD1EC495633FCD63F52</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-string\">uid</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-string\">[ultimate]</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">imcoder</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&lt;1187931389@qq.com&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-string\">sub</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-string\">rsa2048</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2020-03-05</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">[E]</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">[expires:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2022-03-05</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">]</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"hljs-string\">pub</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-string\">rsa2048</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2020-03-05</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">[SC]</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">[expires:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2022-03-05</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">]</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-string\">21A78F78088627FBFDF44B0AF454587F5B01700C</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-string\">uid</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-string\">[ultimate]</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">imcoder</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&lt;1187931389@qq.com&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-string\">sub</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-string\">rsa2048</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2020-03-05</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">[E]</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">[expires:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2022-03-05</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">]</span>\n</pre><p><br></p><h2><strong>配置Maven</strong></h2><p>配置maven有两种方式</p><ol><li><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">依赖oss-parent</span></li><li><span class=\"ql-lineHeight-200\">自己手动配置maven</span></li></ol><p>第一种方式应该比较简单，这里不做过多描述。下面主要针对第二种情况来来发布，起码知道各个配置的作用</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>配置settings.xml</strong></h3><p>sonatype需要身份验证，所以我们需要在settings.xml里配置sonatype的用户名和密码，在&lt;servers&gt;标签下添加一个&lt;server&gt;</p><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">server</span>&gt;</span>\n&nbsp;  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">id</span>&gt;</span>ossrh<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">id</span>&gt;</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">username</span>&gt;</span>sonatype用户名<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">username</span>&gt;</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">password</span>&gt;</span>sonatype密码<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">password</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">server</span>&gt;</span>\n</pre><p><br></p><h3><strong>配置pom.xml</strong></h3><p>pom.xml配置要求很严格，我就因此弄了半天，下面是配置示例</p><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">name</span>&gt;</span>imcoder-base<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">name</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">description</span>&gt;</span>imcoder-base<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">description</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">url</span>&gt;</span>https://github.com/imcoder-cloud/imcoder-base<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">url</span>&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">licenses</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">license</span>&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">name</span>&gt;</span>The Apache Software License, Version 2.0<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">name</span>&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">url</span>&gt;</span>http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.txt<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">url</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">license</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">licenses</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">scm</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">url</span>&gt;</span>https://github.com/imcoder-cloud/imcoder-base<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">url</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">connection</span>&gt;</span>https://github.com/imcoder-cloud/imcoder-base.git<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">connection</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">scm</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">properties</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">maven.compiler.source</span>&gt;<